				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-V%C4%83n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/An-Ho%E1%BA%A1ch-s%C6%A1n-B%C3%A1o-%C3%82n-t%E1%BB%B1-bi-k%C3%BD/poem-VMsZJa3_qA9RQB4PwzHmIQ">An Hoạch sơn Báo Ân tự bi ký - 安獲山報恩寺碑記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-V%C4%83n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-PPHKNipjENvZFLSGPiZIhQ">Chu Văn Thường</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%C3%A1t-ai-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-3-T%E1%BA%B7ng-t%E1%BA%A3-b%E1%BB%99c-x%E1%BA%A1-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-qu%E1%BB%91c-c%C3%B4ng-Nghi%C3%AAm-c%C3%B4ng-V%C5%A9/poem-sw3SLrGVq-mTL0lOgFbZOQ">Bát ai thi kỳ 3 - Tặng tả bộc xạ Trịnh quốc công Nghiêm công Vũ - 八哀詩其三－贈左僕射鄭國公嚴公武</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4n-Ph%E1%BA%A7n/C%E1%BB%95-%C3%BD-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-S5zO6alQc2pkiTRmSDGHbA">Cổ ý kỳ 2 - 古意其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4n-Ph%E1%BA%A7n/author-Qr01DWDfzQiHc7bG-WU6cg">Tôn Phần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/L%E1%BA%A1c-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-n%E1%BB%AF-nhi-h%C3%A0nh/poem-BnmF1CW-HG-Nvl6cafIm6w">Lạc Dương nữ nhi hành - 洛陽女兒行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/Minh-Phi-kh%C3%BAc-ho%E1%BA%A1-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Gi%E1%BB%9Bi-Ph%E1%BB%A7-t%C3%A1c/poem-SAqVQ5Ka7e41T5GXDuBCXQ">Minh Phi khúc, hoạ Vương Giới Phủ tác - 別滁明妃曲和王介甫作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Ngo%C3%A3-ki%E1%BB%81u/poem-27nefcobpV_Df4huKOXKRw">Ngoã kiều - 瓦橋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Quy-tri%E1%BB%81u-hoan/poem-Od9WM7G1UUtUjZm4ypjl3A">Quy triều hoan - 歸朝歡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-V%C4%83n-Ngh%E1%BB%8B-I/Thu%C3%BD-S%C6%A1n-c%C3%BAc/poem-CU9Yj0DviX9JaZgOkP-HWA">Thuý Sơn cúc - 翆山菊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-V%C4%83n-Ngh%E1%BB%8B-I/author-j2yv60iLSGVWsUs_D51NxQ">Phạm Văn Nghị (I)</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tu%C3%BD-ca-h%C3%A0nh-t%E1%BA%B7ng-C%C3%B4ng-An-Nhan-th%E1%BA%ADp-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BB%A7-th%E1%BB%89nh-C%E1%BB%91-b%C3%A1t-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-b%C3%ADch/poem-OmQxrd4OxiuGOfZIDuWp0A">Tuý ca hành tặng Công An Nhan thập thiếu phủ thỉnh Cố bát đề bích - 醉歌行贈公安顏十少府請顧八題壁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ph%C3%B3-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%90%C3%B4-th%E1%BA%A3o-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-trung-h%E1%BB%AFu-t%C3%A1c-ti%C3%AAn-k%C3%BD-Nghi%C3%AAm-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-c%C3%B4ng-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-9xlmaMxSRK2hSmmGOC2T8w">Tương phó Thành Đô thảo đường đồ trung hữu tác, tiên ký Nghiêm Trịnh công kỳ 4 - 將赴成都草堂途中有作，先寄嚴鄭公其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
